<emphasis id="BD6AFD32267DABDD6148D403B2626091" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Holotype</emphasis>
: male (IZCAS), Koththol Lena (= cave) (
<geoCoordinate id="D4BC75656A77770C4388051D0037CF68" degrees="6" direction="north" minutes="54.22" orientation="latitude" precision="9" value="6.9036665">6°54.22'N</geoCoordinate>
